{"type": "article", "id": 27229, "title": "了解狗狗心情的束带装置", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-24T06:49:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132412ZexKcOo9i8dazAwV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>由于我们并不能通过语言直接同汪星人交流，要了解它们的内心世界不是件容易的事情。日本的软件工程师 Joji Yamaguchi 为此设计了一款可以视觉化汪星人心情的束带装置 <a href=\"http://inupathy.com/\">Inupathy</a>，它通过内置的心率传感器来检测狗狗的心跳，以此分析出狗狗的心情并通过 LED 灯的颜色变化反映出来。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132408wLNj5ri3KfBupMaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021324098ZxBtjUyHz9pFKnO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132409g6AtjX4wzP2Z7DYl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132410Iixlv74hkGS2LeOq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}